109
00:07:01,760 --> 00:07:02,760
Life is unpredictable

110
00:07:03,280 --> 00:07:04,200
The world is full of surprises

111
00:07:05,360 --> 00:07:07,280
Who can ever be mentally prepared for it?

112
00:07:09,640 --> 00:07:10,440
Yeah

113
00:07:11,560 --> 00:07:12,720
Some things...

114
00:07:14,040 --> 00:07:15,480
