115
00:07:24,480 --> 00:07:25,280
We're here

116
00:07:27,240 --> 00:07:28,040
Let's get out

117
00:07:30,800 --> 00:07:32,360
Boss, five bowls of noodles

118
00:07:32,360 --> 00:07:33,560
One without chili

119
00:07:34,200 --> 00:07:35,360
