122
00:07:39,480 --> 00:07:40,240
Have a seat

123
00:07:40,360 --> 00:07:41,360
We're back again

124
00:07:41,600 --> 00:07:42,560
Welcome, welcome!

125
00:07:44,960 --> 00:07:45,760
Boss

126
00:07:45,920 --> 00:07:47,600
