127
00:07:47,600 --> 00:07:48,240
Sure

128
00:07:52,160 --> 00:07:52,960
Here's your pickled garlic

129
00:07:52,960 --> 00:07:53,720
More if you need it

130
00:07:54,000 --> 00:07:54,400
Okay, okay

131
00:07:54,400 --> 00:07:55,080
Thanks, boss

132
00:07:57,080 --> 00:07:59,280
Before the noodles get here

133
00:08:00,360 --> 00:08:02,080
I've got something to tell you

134
00:08:02,520 --> 00:08:05,320
Ever since the Zhang Wei incident

135
00:08:05,320 --> 00:08:07,560
business at Xiao Xi Tian

136
00:08:07,560 --> 00:08:09,040
has been getting worse and worse

137
00:08:10,400 --> 00:08:12,040
This line of work...

138
00:08:12,040 --> 00:08:13,680
I've been at it for decades

139
00:08:13,960 --> 00:08:16,880
