140
00:08:18,360 --> 00:08:20,480
Times have changed, you know

141
00:08:20,720 --> 00:08:23,440
Even good wine needs advertising

142
00:08:24,120 --> 00:08:24,920
So

143
00:08:24,920 --> 00:08:26,720
So you've decided

144
00:08:26,720 --> 00:08:29,280
to renovate Xiao Xi Tian

145
00:08:29,280 --> 00:08:30,280
right?

146
00:08:30,280 --> 00:08:32,680
With comprehension skills like yours

147
00:08:33,600 --> 00:08:35,280
no wonder you went to junior college

148
00:08:37,840 --> 00:08:38,560
Ha

149
00:08:41,320 --> 00:08:42,600
Let me tell you

150
00:08:43,000 --> 00:08:45,040
loyalty is often found among the lowly

151
00:08:45,040 --> 00:08:47,240
while betrayal comes from the educated

152
00:08:47,440 --> 00:08:48,720
You think I can't recite poetry?

153
00:08:50,320 --> 00:08:53,040
Reciting poems doesn't mean you're educated

154
00:08:53,040 --> 00:08:54,480
Here we go again, here we go again

155
00:08:54,480 --> 00:08:55,440
Let's get to the point

156
00:08:55,800 --> 00:08:56,960
What I mean is

157
00:08:57,720 --> 00:08:59,520
