169
00:09:22,600 --> 00:09:24,720
asking if anyone died today

170
00:09:25,640 --> 00:09:26,680
And besides

171
00:09:26,920 --> 00:09:29,760
we can't very well hope for

172
00:09:29,760 --> 00:09:32,760
