173
00:09:33,440 --> 00:09:35,480
Who told you to say that?

174
00:09:35,800 --> 00:09:37,760
Use your brains for once

175
00:09:40,040 --> 00:09:41,120
Actually

176
00:09:41,120 --> 00:09:42,880
