179
00:09:46,920 --> 00:09:48,440
And if that really doesn't work

180
00:09:49,400 --> 00:09:51,160
why not try the most traditional method?

181
00:09:52,080 --> 00:09:53,080
What method?

182
00:09:59,080 --> 00:09:59,880
Excuse me, miss

183
00:10:00,760 --> 00:10:02,320
Hey handsome, want to add me on WeChat?

184
00:10:03,800 --> 00:10:05,160
Xiao Xi Tian, one-stop service

185
00:10:05,160 --> 00:10:06,840
Check out our funeral packages

186
