Funeral packages, my foot!

187
00:10:08,600 --> 00:10:09,120
Are you out of your mind?

188
00:10:09,120 --> 00:10:10,280
I'm this young and you're wishing me dead?

189
00:10:11,240 --> 00:10:11,720
What's so funny?

190
00:10:11,720 --> 00:10:12,240
You're crazy too

191
00:10:16,480 --> 00:10:17,840
She's calling you crazy too

192
00:10:18,000 --> 00:10:19,000
What are you laughing at?

193
00:10:19,000 --> 00:10:19,760
Nutcase

194
00:10:21,200 --> 00:10:23,800
Hi, Xiao Xi Tian, one-stop funeral service

195
00:10:23,800 --> 00:10:25,200
Care to take a look?

196
00:10:25,200 --> 00:10:26,840
Check out our funeral services

197
00:10:28,240 --> 00:10:29,640
Screw loose in the head

198
00:10:40,280 --> 00:10:41,480
Oh, Xu

199
00:10:41,480 --> 00:10:43,480
You might as well die soon

200
00:10:43,480 --> 00:10:44,400
Look at the state you're in

201
00:10:44,400 --> 00:10:46,120
Still pining over that hussy out there

202
00:10:46,120 --> 00:10:47,120
I see you pining every single day

203
00:10:47,120 --> 00:10:48,000
Sorry to bother you

204
00:10:48,000 --> 00:10:50,240
Our full-service package is 20% off

205
00:10:50,240 --> 00:10:51,880
What, full-service?

206
00:10:52,440 --> 00:10:54,960
And free 24-hour house calls too

207
00:10:55,360 --> 00:10:56,520
Free house calls?

208
00:10:57,640 --> 00:10:58,600
Get out of my way

209
00:10:58,600 --> 00:11:00,000
Young man, is it you?

210
00:11:01,680 --> 00:11:02,600
I'll teach you to pine

211
00:11:02,600 --> 00:11:03,920
Pining every single day

212
00:11:03,920 --> 00:11:05,320
Pining, always pining

213
00:11:05,320 --> 00:11:06,520
Pining over that hussy

214
00:11:06,840 --> 00:11:07,800
Stop hitting him

215
00:11:07,800 --> 00:11:09,480
That young man seduced me

216
00:11:10,280 --> 00:11:11,160
I'll beat you to death

217
00:11:13,360 --> 00:11:14,240
I'll beat you to death

218
00:11:14,920 --> 00:11:15,880
Go, go, hurry up

219
00:11:16,400 --> 00:11:17,680
Hurry, hurry, let's go, Yiran

220
00:11:23,120 --> 00:11:24,160
I'll just beat you to death

221
00:11:25,320 --> 00:11:26,280
Stop hitting me

222
00:11:26,720 --> 00:11:28,240
I meant that other guy

223
00:11:28,240 --> 00:11:29,760
I didn't ask for a woman

224
00:11:31,440 --> 00:11:32,040
Help!

225
00:11:32,600 --> 00:11:34,840
