226
00:11:34,960 --> 00:11:35,680
Here, here, come on

227
00:11:35,680 --> 00:11:36,680
Thanks

228
00:11:36,680 --> 00:11:38,000
Here you go

229
00:11:39,240 --> 00:11:40,920
Leave this whole thing to me

230
00:11:40,920 --> 00:11:41,920
You're the best

231
00:11:42,760 --> 00:11:44,680
How about we all take a group photo?

232
00:11:44,680 --> 00:11:45,160
Sure

233
00:11:45,160 --> 00:11:45,960
Just as I thought

234
00:11:46,440 --> 00:11:48,440
Hard work is worthless next to talent

235
00:11:49,080 --> 00:11:51,000
