236
00:11:51,800 --> 00:11:53,400
Okay, everyone look at the camera

237
00:11:53,400 --> 00:11:54,720
Maybe that's a good thing

238
00:11:54,720 --> 00:11:55,560
Get ready

239
00:11:55,560 --> 00:11:57,040
Did you forget what Uncle Chen said?

240
00:11:57,560 --> 00:11:58,800
