241
00:11:58,800 --> 00:12:01,080
Say cheese

242
00:12:01,080 --> 00:12:03,840
Bad business means a low death rate

243
00:12:04,120 --> 00:12:05,200
That's a good thing

244
00:12:08,680 --> 00:12:09,400
True enough

245
00:12:10,480 --> 00:12:12,400
Then here's to everyone living a long life

246
00:12:13,760 --> 00:12:16,080
