247
00:12:16,080 --> 00:12:19,000
I'll make every one of you look gorgeous

248
00:12:19,000 --> 00:12:20,680
Thanks, thanks

249
00:12:33,800 --> 00:12:34,880
Hurry, hurry!

250
00:12:35,000 --> 00:12:36,080
