265
00:13:26,400 --> 00:13:27,440
Stop right there!

266
00:13:44,560 --> 00:13:45,280
Hey, buddy

267
00:13:45,600 --> 00:13:46,400
I'm sorry, I'm so sorry

268
00:13:46,400 --> 00:13:47,240
Are you okay?

269
00:13:47,240 --> 00:13:48,800
Get up, let me take you to the hospital

270
00:13:48,800 --> 00:13:49,560
