283
00:14:14,320 --> 00:14:15,280
Hey, buddy

284
00:14:15,280 --> 00:14:16,120
I'm sorry

285
00:14:16,120 --> 00:14:16,600
You... you...

286
00:14:16,600 --> 00:14:17,640
Tell me how much you lost

287
00:14:17,640 --> 00:14:18,400
Let me pay you back

288
00:14:18,640 --> 00:14:19,800
Really, I...

289
00:14:21,760 --> 00:14:23,000
Forget it, you didn't mean to

290
00:14:23,000 --> 00:14:23,520
You...

291
00:14:23,520 --> 00:14:24,040
It wasn't me

292
00:14:24,040 --> 00:14:25,120
Someone snatched my phone

293
00:14:25,120 --> 00:14:26,160
That guy just now grabbed it

294
00:14:26,160 --> 00:14:27,280
Really, I'm not a con artist

295
00:14:27,280 --> 00:14:28,320
It really got stolen

296
00:14:29,640 --> 00:14:30,800
Here, buddy

