00:25:35,160 --> 00:25:36,040
Wu Huilan

595
00:25:36,040 --> 00:25:37,120
Where are your tears?

596
00:25:37,120 --> 00:25:38,480
Aren't you supposed to be a great crier?

597
00:25:38,600 --> 00:25:40,120
Hold on, Team Leader Chen

598
00:25:40,520 --> 00:25:42,760
I'm a professional funeral wailer

599
00:25:42,760 --> 00:25:45,320
It's a wedding, how am I supposed to cry?

600
00:25:45,960 --> 00:25:47,240
Isn't it all the same?

601
00:25:47,600 --> 00:25:48,640
It's all just acting

602
00:25:48,640 --> 00:25:49,600
What's the difference?

603
00:25:50,200 --> 00:25:51,040
Huge difference!

604
00:25:51,400 --> 00:25:52,320
That money of yours

605
00:25:52,720 --> 00:25:53,720
Eight hundred!

606
00:25:53,720 --> 00:25:55,200
I already sent it to that Zhang Lijuan

607
00:25:55,200 --> 00:25:56,280
You gave me eight hundred?

608
00:25:56,280 --> 00:25:56,760
Eight hundred

609
00:25:58,320 --> 00:25:59,600
That damn Zhang Lijuan!

610
00:25:59,600 --> 00:26:00,400
Wu Huilan

611
00:26:00,960 --> 00:26:01,960
Give me an explanation

612
00:26:01,960 --> 00:26:02,760
What's going on here?

613
00:26:03,000 --> 00:26:03,880
Let me tell you

614
00:26:03,880 --> 00:26:05,320
This is a bit complicated

615
00:26:05,320 --> 00:26:06,720
I originally came here to wail at a funeral

616
00:26:06,920 --> 00:26:07,600
What are you doing?

617
00:26:08,320 --> 00:26:10,880
Auntie, why'd you show up dressed like that?

618
00:26:11,800 --> 00:26:13,560
Weren't you the one who called me to wail?

619
00:26:15,040 --> 00:26:16,520
"Rest in peace with a smile"

620
00:26:16,760 --> 00:26:18,400
What funeral wailing?

621
00:26:18,400 --> 00:26:19,640
Today's my big day

622
00:26:19,640 --> 00:26:20,960
Let's not say such unlucky things

623
00:26:23,920 --> 00:26:25,320
Sorry, sorry

624
00:26:25,320 --> 00:26:26,080
Good luck and good fortune!

625
00:26:26,080 --> 00:26:27,200
No taboos at all, no taboos!

626
00:26:27,200 --> 00:26:28,120
It's fine, Auntie

627
00:26:28,120 --> 00:26:29,160
Just listen to me

628
00:26:29,160 --> 00:26:30,280
Hurry up and change your clothes

629
00:26:30,480 --> 00:26:32,160
Your role today is to play my mom

630
00:26:32,280 --> 00:26:33,120
I play your mom?

631
00:26:33,760 --> 00:26:36,120
Me?

632
00:26:37,120 --> 00:26:39,440
It's your wedding, why isn't your mom here herself?

633
00:26:40,320 --> 00:26:41,120
My mom

634
00:26:47,920 --> 00:26:48,880
What's wrong with you?

635
00:26:49,160 --> 00:26:50,560
My mom's gravely ill in bed

636
00:26:51,240 --> 00:26:52,800
So she can't make it here

637
00:26:53,240 --> 00:26:54,400
My wife said

638
00:26:54,400 --> 00:26:56,120
if there's no mom at the wedding,

639
00:26:56,560 --> 00:26:58,120
she'll lose face, you know

640
00:26:58,360 --> 00:27:00,080
It took me so long to get married

641
00:27:02,920 --> 00:27:04,560
I'm begging you here

642
00:27:09,520 --> 00:27:10,680
Come on, don't cry now

643
00:27:11,360 --> 00:27:12,440
A grown man like you,

644
00:27:12,440 --> 00:27:13,800
what's there to cry about?

645
00:27:13,800 --> 00:27:14,320
Come on

646
00:27:15,600 --> 00:27:17,320
Whatever it is, take your time and tell me

647
00:27:17,720 --> 00:27:18,640
I'll pay you extra

648
00:27:22,640 --> 00:27:23,240
Five hundred

649
00:27:23,720 --> 00:27:25,440
Once you change clothes, come right over

650
00:27:25,560 --> 00:27:26,040
That's settled then

651
00:27:26,040 --> 00:27:26,920
Wait a second

652
00:27:28,880 --> 00:27:29,680
Six hundred

653
00:27:31,200 --> 00:27:32,480
Fine, six hundred it is

654
00:27:32,720 --> 00:27:34,120
Six is a lucky number, right?

655
00:27:34,120 --> 00:27:35,240
Thanks so much, Auntie

656
00:27:35,240 --> 00:27:36,120
Thank you

657
00:27:36,440 --> 00:27:37,520
And then?

658
00:27:37,520 --> 00:27:39,040
And then you saw the rest, didn't you?

659
00:27:39,040 --> 00:27:41,840
I went up and played the groom's mom

660
00:27:42,040 --> 00:27:43,600
Just doing whatever they told you

661
00:27:43,600 --> 00:27:44,680
Are you out of your mind?

662
00:27:44,680 --> 00:27:46,360
What's that supposed to mean, Li Yiran?

663
00:27:46,520 --> 00:27:48,200
I made a thousand bucks today

664
00:27:48,400 --> 00:27:50,040
A thousand bucks, you get that?

665
00:27:50,640 --> 00:27:52,320
Still, you can't take just any money

666
00:27:52,320 --> 00:27:53,320
Take a look at that groom

667
00:27:53,320 --> 00:27:54,640
One look and you know he's a con man

668
00:27:55,440 --> 00:27:57,000
The groom's a con man?

669
00:27:57,840 --> 00:27:58,760
Let me take a look

670
00:28:01,200 --> 00:28:01,480
Come on

671
00:28:01,480 --> 00:28:03,240
The moment I got there, something felt off

672
00:28:03,840 --> 00:28:05,320
Someone genuinely getting married,

673
00:28:05,320 --> 00:28:07,520
why hire fake parents and groomsmen to act?

674
00:28:08,160 --> 00:28:10,800
Most people there looked like strangers

675
00:28:10,800 --> 00:28:12,000
This whole wedding

676
00:28:12,000 --> 00:28:13,160
is just a scam

677
00:28:13,240 --> 00:28:14,040
Handing it out

678
00:28:16,040 --> 00:28:17,680
Yeah, something's not right

679
00:28:18,080 --> 00:28:19,680
Why are they handing out money?

680
00:28:22,240 --> 00:28:23,240
How'd you figure it out?

681
00:28:23,240 --> 00:28:24,440
How could I not figure it out?

682
00:28:24,560 --> 00:28:26,080
I used my eyes, obviously

683
00:28:26,240 --> 00:28:28,960
Now the bride and groom will exchange rings

684
00:28:35,840 --> 00:28:37,840
Okay

685
00:28:38,600 --> 00:28:40,680
That damn con man

686
00:28:40,680 --> 00:28:43,120
Now, the groom may kiss the bride

687
00:28:43,280 --> 00:28:44,640
May you soon have a child

688
00:28:46,520 --> 00:28:57,560
Kiss her! Kiss her!

689
00:28:57,560 --> 00:28:58,440
No kissing allowed!

690
00:29:06,040 --> 00:29:06,840
Sis

691
00:29:07,280 --> 00:29:07,800
Come here

692
00:29:07,800 --> 00:29:08,840
What's this about?

693
00:29:08,840 --> 00:29:09,680
No idea

694
00:29:09,800 --> 00:29:11,040
Everyone, listen to me

695
00:29:11,480 --> 00:29:12,840
My name is Wu Huilan

696
00:29:14,680 --> 00:29:16,240
This is my ID card

697
00:29:16,440 --> 00:29:18,000
I'm filing a formal complaint

698
00:29:18,000 --> 00:29:20,480
This wedding today is a marriage scam

699
00:29:21,080 --> 00:29:21,920
A scam!

700
00:29:22,920 --> 00:29:23,640
Get down here

701
00:29:23,640 --> 00:29:25,160
Should... should we keep filming?

702
00:29:26,640 --> 00:29:27,600
We already took the money

703
00:29:27,600 --> 00:29:28,240
Keep filming

704
00:29:28,240 --> 00:29:28,840
Film it

705
00:29:29,640 --> 00:29:30,600
Let me tell you all

706
00:29:31,000 --> 00:29:32,240
I'm not his mother

707
00:29:32,240 --> 00:29:33,440
I'm not his mother

708
00:29:33,720 --> 00:29:35,080
Today I actually came here

709
00:29:35,080 --> 00:29:36,200
to attend a funeral

710
00:29:36,440 --> 00:29:38,040
I was supposed to come mourn today

711
00:29:38,440 --> 00:29:39,720
But then this guy right here

712
00:29:39,720 --> 00:29:41,360
He gave me 600 yuan

713
00:29:41,440 --> 00:29:42,960
to play his mother

714
00:29:42,960 --> 00:29:43,680
I'm not kidding

715
00:29:43,680 --> 00:29:44,760
I may be short on cash

716
00:29:44,760 --> 00:29:47,000
but I won't take money against my conscience

717
00:29:47,000 --> 00:29:48,360
I already paid you

718
00:29:48,400 --> 00:29:49,040
Scram

719
00:29:49,320 --> 00:29:50,480
You damn con artist

720
00:29:50,880 --> 00:29:52,440
He's not my son

721
00:29:52,720 --> 00:29:53,920
I don't have a son

722
00:29:53,920 --> 00:29:55,200
And I don't have a husband either

723
00:29:55,200 --> 00:29:57,080
My husband died a long time ago

724
00:29:57,080 --> 00:29:57,440
Wu Huilan!

725
00:29:57,440 --> 00:29:58,480
They're all con artists

726
00:29:58,480 --> 00:30:00,760
Mr. Zhou, your dad was right

727
00:30:01,040 --> 00:30:02,880
Chen Xiaofang's family brings you bad luck

728
00:30:03,440 --> 00:30:05,320
This is a huge job for Xidongdong

729
00:30:05,320 --> 00:30:06,160
What do we do now?

730
00:30:06,640 --> 00:30:07,320
Xu Wumei

731
00:30:07,640 --> 00:30:09,440
Did you know all along this was a scam?

732
00:30:11,200 --> 00:30:11,920
Me?

733
00:30:12,720 --> 00:30:13,440
I had no idea

734
00:30:13,440 --> 00:30:14,160
I'm filing a formal complaint

735
00:30:14,160 --> 00:30:16,480
You dumb woman, didn't I pay you?

736
00:30:16,680 --> 00:30:17,760
You came to ruin everything for me

737
00:30:17,760 --> 00:30:18,920
Come at me! Come at me!

738
00:30:18,920 --> 00:30:20,400
Guys, someone's making trouble

739
00:30:20,400 --> 00:30:20,720
Get her!

740
00:30:20,720 --> 00:30:21,720
Go on, hit me!

741
00:30:26,120 --> 00:30:26,760
Stop hitting!

742
00:30:27,080 --> 00:30:27,720
Stop hitting them!

743
00:30:28,160 --> 00:30:28,680
Brother-in-law

744
00:30:28,920 --> 00:30:29,520
Mr. Zhou

745
00:30:30,240 --> 00:30:31,800
The balance hasn't been paid yet

746
00:30:31,800 --> 00:30:33,120
To hell with your balance

747
00:30:33,120 --> 00:30:34,040
My brother-in-law

748
00:30:34,040 --> 00:30:34,480
matters most

749
00:30:34,480 --> 00:30:35,280
Stop hitting!

750
00:30:35,280 --> 00:30:35,920
Brother-in-law

751
00:30:40,040 --> 00:30:41,120
Get back here now

752
00:30:41,120 --> 00:30:42,200
What do you think you're doing?

753
00:30:43,600 --> 00:30:45,000
I'll take you down with me!

754
00:31:11,360 --> 00:31:12,160
Zhou Fang

755
00:31:13,400 --> 00:31:14,520
I'm hurt

756
00:31:14,520 --> 00:31:15,240
It hurts like hell

757
00:31:15,240 --> 00:31:16,120
I need to go to the hospital

758
00:31:17,120 --> 00:31:18,360
Then hurry up and go

759
00:31:18,440 --> 00:31:19,640
If you don't go now

760
00:31:19,640 --> 00:31:20,760
your wound will heal on its own

761
00:31:22,760 --> 00:31:23,640
I'm so furious

762
00:31:24,840 --> 00:31:26,560
I figured those people were unreliable

763
00:31:26,840 --> 00:31:28,880
but I didn't expect them to trash the whole place

764
00:31:29,040 --> 00:31:30,080
And you're still laughing

765
00:31:30,240 --> 00:31:32,240
The final payment isn't even settled

766
00:31:32,280 --> 00:31:34,000
That wailing mourner, Wu Huilan

767
00:31:34,000 --> 00:31:35,160
and that scriptwriter, Li Yiran

768
00:31:35,160 --> 00:31:35,840
It's all their fault

769
00:31:36,800 --> 00:31:38,440
The final payment is no big deal

770
00:31:38,600 --> 00:31:40,120
I run a wedding company

771
00:31:40,120 --> 00:31:41,680
not just to make money, you know

772
00:31:41,680 --> 00:31:43,480
Then how will you explain this to your dad?

773
00:31:43,680 --> 00:31:44,760
That's not the point

774
00:31:44,840 --> 00:31:46,240
The point is that today

775
00:31:46,240 --> 00:31:48,880
I got hurt because of my brother-in-law

776
00:31:49,640 --> 00:31:51,720
No way Xiaofang won't feel sorry for me

777
00:31:52,160 --> 00:31:53,720
I'm going to find her right now

778
00:31:54,040 --> 00:31:56,320
Did Xiaofang save your life in a past life?

779
00:31:56,320 --> 00:31:57,280
You've got love on the brain

780
00:32:00,320 --> 00:32:01,320
Are you crazy?

781
00:32:01,520 --> 00:32:03,040
Having my brother host a wedding

782
00:32:03,040 --> 00:32:04,080
What were you thinking?

783
00:32:04,400 --> 00:32:05,760
Wasn't it you who said it?

784
00:32:06,080 --> 00:32:07,520
Investing is about hedging

785
00:32:07,520 --> 00:32:08,880
and luck is about balance

786
00:32:09,240 --> 00:32:10,560
Someone in the funeral business

787
00:32:10,560 --> 00:32:13,320
should do some wedding work to offset it

788
00:32:21,000 --> 00:32:23,760
I got hurt today because of my brother-in-law

789
00:32:23,760 --> 00:32:24,440
Look

790
00:32:25,400 --> 00:32:26,320
Come here, let me see

791
00:32:32,000 --> 00:32:32,800
It hurts this bad?

792
00:32:32,800 --> 00:32:33,480
It hurts

793
00:32:36,240 --> 00:32:37,480
A little blow and it won't hurt anymore

794
00:32:42,200 --> 00:32:43,240
Let me put some medicine on it

795
00:32:49,560 --> 00:32:50,480
There's more over here

796
00:33:01,080 --> 00:33:02,440
Don't get all cheeky with me

797
00:33:07,080 --> 00:33:08,600
It's fine, it's fine

798
00:33:09,000 --> 00:33:10,360
It's okay, it's okay

799
00:33:11,800 --> 00:33:12,800
Don't, don't be scared, Xiaofang

800
00:33:12,800 --> 00:33:14,120
Don't be scared

801
00:33:14,480 --> 00:33:15,360
Don't be scared

802
00:33:16,960 --> 00:33:18,040
Sounds like thunder outside

803
00:33:18,040 --> 00:33:19,240
Thunder and rain both

804
00:33:20,400 --> 00:33:22,200
Then why don't you just stay tonight?

805
00:33:24,000 --> 00:33:24,800
Sure

806
00:33:25,600 --> 00:33:26,720
That was worth it

807
00:33:26,840 --> 00:33:27,640
What did you say?

808
00:33:29,880 --> 00:33:31,800
I said, whatever you say

809
00:33:32,080 --> 00:33:32,880
Okay

810
00:33:33,760 --> 00:33:35,200
Then you can sleep on the couch tonight

811
00:33:37,680 --> 00:33:38,520
But I'm injured

812
00:33:38,520 --> 00:33:39,800
And this is how you treat me?

813
00:33:41,720 --> 00:33:42,720
A favor deserves a favor

814
00:33:43,640 --> 00:33:45,520
I'll get my brother to keep you company

815
00:33:45,520 --> 00:33:46,040
No, no

816
00:33:46,040 --> 00:33:47,480
Bro, bro

817
00:33:47,800 --> 00:33:48,480
Don't wake him up

818
00:33:48,480 --> 00:33:49,040
Bro

819
00:33:49,040 --> 00:33:49,840
No, no

820
00:33:50,280 --> 00:33:51,240
Are you asleep yet?

821
00:33:54,680 --> 00:33:56,520
Fine, the couch works too

822
00:33:56,720 --> 00:33:57,800
At least I'm staying at their place

823
00:34:02,640 --> 00:34:03,480
Yiran

824
00:34:05,200 --> 00:34:06,040
Yiran

825
00:34:06,720 --> 00:34:08,000
Come on, don't be mad

826
00:34:18,680 --> 00:34:19,560
All right, enough

827
00:34:20,000 --> 00:34:21,280
You've been sulking forever

828
00:34:24,960 --> 00:34:26,720
Who was it that promised me

829
00:34:26,720 --> 00:34:27,840
they wouldn't cause trouble?

830
00:34:29,480 --> 00:34:30,240
Well, this

831
00:34:31,360 --> 00:34:32,600
doesn't really count as trouble

832
00:34:32,800 --> 00:34:34,560
Your own life is a total mess,

833
00:34:34,560 --> 00:34:36,000
and you still worry about others?

834
00:34:39,600 --> 00:34:41,920
Every kid is their parents' pride and joy

835
00:34:41,920 --> 00:34:43,120
I couldn't just stand there and watch

836
00:34:43,120 --> 00:34:44,480
that bride get taken in by a con man

837
00:34:44,480 --> 00:34:45,360
I just couldn't help it

838
00:34:45,600 --> 00:34:46,760
Didn't I tell you

839
00:34:46,760 --> 00:34:47,760
to stop being a busybody?

840
00:34:47,760 --> 00:34:49,200
To stop being a busybody!

841
00:34:50,240 --> 00:34:52,040
But marriage is a huge life event

842
00:34:52,040 --> 00:34:53,480
That's hardly a trivial matter

843
00:34:55,280 --> 00:34:56,040
Wu Huilan,

844
00:34:57,720 --> 00:34:59,160
do you know that meddling in others' fate

845
00:34:59,160 --> 00:35:00,520
comes with a price?

846
00:35:03,040 --> 00:35:04,360
What price is that, exactly?

847
00:35:05,080 --> 00:35:06,000
Your dad and I,

848
00:35:06,000 --> 00:35:08,160
if we'd overthought it back then, you wouldn't exist

849
00:35:08,160 --> 00:35:10,360
A lot of things, you just can't overthink them

850
00:35:10,360 --> 00:35:11,280
You get it?

851
00:35:11,920 --> 00:35:12,720
And that's exactly why this family

852
00:35:12,720 --> 00:35:14,320
ended up the way it is now

853
00:35:24,600 --> 00:35:26,000
A ruined wedding

854
00:35:27,240 --> 00:35:29,400
beats a whole lifetime that's ruined

855
00:35:30,840 --> 00:35:32,400
I just wanted to save her

856
00:35:32,400 --> 00:35:34,240
I don't even know what I did wrong

857
00:35:50,280 --> 00:35:51,080
Let's go home

858
00:36:30,160 --> 00:36:31,760
What son of a bitch did this?

859
00:36:32,880 --> 00:36:34,680
Guts to do it, but no guts to own up?

860
00:36:35,680 --> 00:36:37,160
I curse your entire ancestral line!

861
00:36:37,160 --> 00:36:38,320
May your kids be born without assholes!

862
00:36:41,120 --> 00:36:42,640
If you're this bored, go get a job

863
00:36:42,640 --> 00:36:44,320
Every day just piling more work on me

864
00:36:46,440 --> 00:36:47,240
Xiaofang

865
00:36:49,680 --> 00:36:50,600
What are you doing here?

866
00:36:51,360 --> 00:36:52,720
Perfect timing. Help me clean this up

867
00:36:54,480 --> 00:36:55,640
You don't need to do this yourself

868
00:36:56,040 --> 00:36:56,880
Leave it to me

869
00:37:17,240 --> 00:37:18,800
Halt

870
00:37:19,400 --> 00:37:20,520
Right face

871
00:37:22,080 --> 00:37:23,520
Hello, boss

872
00:37:24,160 --> 00:37:25,280
Hello, Mr. Zhou

873
00:37:25,600 --> 00:37:26,280
Let's get to work

874
00:37:39,040 --> 00:37:39,560
Xiaofang

875
00:37:40,200 --> 00:37:41,000
It's okay

876
00:37:41,640 --> 00:37:42,680
As long as you want it

877
00:37:42,960 --> 00:37:44,040
As long as I can give it

878
00:37:46,240 --> 00:37:47,280
Just sit down and relax first

879
00:37:50,480 --> 00:37:51,440
Who did this?

880
00:37:52,080 --> 00:37:53,320
You've got the nerve to ask?

881
00:37:53,480 --> 00:37:55,160
They found out we hired funeral guys

882
00:37:55,160 --> 00:37:56,320
to wreck their wedding

883
00:37:56,320 --> 00:37:57,560
